The files in this directory are derived from Aider v0.86.1 and have been
modified for use in CodeContextCrafter. See FORK_INFO.md for a detailed
explanation of the modifications.

Major modifications include:
- Removed caching mechanisms for deterministic behavior
- Removed token budget optimization to include all files
- Increased line truncation limit from 100 to 1000 characters
- Added sig_detailed configuration option
- Adjusted import paths for CodeContextCrafter package structure
